snippet.textDisplay:
I saw this in recommendations, earlier I had heard Atif Aslam, Mulazim Hussain, Fizza Javed, Mai Dhai, Gul Panrra, Ali Sethi,  Abida Parveen, Rahat Fateh Ali Khan, Shazia Manzoor, Rizwaan, Muazzam, Mekal Hassan Band. So I thought - this has kinda good no. of views, let's give it a try. It was all good for me when Samra khan was singing, okay, yeah, I think its going to be another one of the descent songs from Coke Studio, but then this douche-bag started singing and my mood was devastated, it was horrifying, I suddenly unplugged the headphones and threw them on the floor (fortunately, it was working in good condition when I later checked it). I muted the laptop and glanced for a minute towards the window, my face all drenched in weird facial expressions of weariness, disgust, shame and anger. I got up, washed my face, and them saw this "el terrible"'s name and swear to myself that I would never ever clickbait to this guy, even it was Coke studio. 
True Story.
